00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:44,958
Scott: Let's talk a little bit here.

104
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:47,477
Scott: My original mouse that I had... Well, okay.

105
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:49,480
Scott: I first had an IBM whatever, right?

106
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,480
Scott: And I had like a Mac mouse with one button.

