00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:13,420
Rym: See, move forward, I use the same setup.

199
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,380
Scott: And then like, that's the other thing.

200
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:15,899
Scott: I use like Q to go fast.

